                      <span>Safety comes at cost of privacy - shared rooms</span>
                    </div>
                    <div className="rounded bg-teal-50 p-2 border border-teal-200">
                      <p className="text-lg font-bold text-teal-700">15,000 - 20,000 AED</p>
                    </div>
