                                  <p className="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">{keyword.intent}</p>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          ))}
                        </div>
                      </ScrollArea>
                    </TabsContent>
                  </Tabs>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>

              {/* Key Thematic Sections */}
              <div className="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                {/* Aesthetic Medicine */}
                <Card className="glass-card border-rose-200">
                  <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                    <CardTitle className="text-sm text-rose-900 flex items-center gap-2">
                      <Sparkles className="h-4 w-4" />
                      Aesthetic Medicine Hub
                    </CardTitle>
                  </CardHeader>
                  <CardContent>
                    <p className="text-xs text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-2">
                      Abu Dhabi and Dubai are global hubs for aesthetic medicine. Dermatology captured <strong>31%</strong> of medical-tourist spend in 2024.
                    </p>
                    <ul className="space-y-1 text-xs text-slate-600">
                      <li>• Deep-plane facelift: $13,500 (vs $23,000 in New York)</li>
                      <li>• High-def VASER liposuction trending</li>
                      <li>• Robotic hair transplants in high demand</li>
                      <li>• &quot;Baby Botox&quot; for subtle enhancements</li>
                    </ul>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>

                {/* Wellness & Beauty */}
                <Card className="glass-card border-pink-200">
                  <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                    <CardTitle className="text-sm text-pink-900 flex items-center gap-2">
                      <Heart className="h-4 w-4" />
                      Beauty from Within
                    </CardTitle>
                  </CardHeader>
                  <CardContent>
                    <p className="text-xs text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-2">
                      The emergence of holistic wellness where health and aesthetics are inextricably linked.
                    </p>
                    <ul className="space-y-1 text-xs text-slate-600">
                      <li>• Science-backed supplements for longevity</li>
                      <li>• Microbiome-balancing gummies and collagen</li>
                      <li>• K-Beauty brands dominate local retail</li>
                      <li>• Clean beauty: paraben-free, sulfate-free</li>
                    </ul>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>

                {/* Workforce Dynamics */}
                <Card className="glass-card border-denim-200">
                  <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                    <CardTitle className="text-sm text-denim-900 flex items-center gap-2">
                      <Users className="h-4 w-4" />
                      Workforce & Licensing
                    </CardTitle>
                  </CardHeader>
                  <CardContent>
                    <p className="text-xs text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-2">
                      Pearson VUE is the exclusive partner for DOH/HAAD exams, assessing competency across multiple domains.
                    </p>
                    <ul className="space-y-1 text-xs text-slate-600">
                      <li>• High demand for Critical Care, ER, OR nurses</li>
                      <li>• Binary Pass/Fail scoring system</li>
                      <li>• Results take 3-5 business days in TAMM</li>
                      <li>• Primary source verification required</li>
                    </ul>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>

                {/* Insurance & Regulation */}
                <Card className="glass-card border-orange-200">
                  <CardHeader className="pb-2">
                    <CardTitle className="text-sm text-orange-900 flex items-center gap-2">
                      <Shield className="h-4 w-4" />
                      Cost of Compliance
                    </CardTitle>
                  </CardHeader>
                  <CardContent>
                    <p className="text-xs text-slate-700 leading-relaxed mb-2">
                      Mandatory health insurance with complex regulatory landscape of fines and appeals.
                    </p>
                    <ul className="space-y-1 text-xs text-slate-600">
                      <li>• AED 300-500 monthly penalty for no coverage</li>
                      <li>• AED 2,000 fine for appeals against violations</li>
                      <li>• HTA guidelines raised market access bar</li>
                      <li>• TAMM platform digitized appeal process</li>
                    </ul>
                  </CardContent>
                </Card>
              </div>

              {/* Strategic Conclusions */}
              <Card className="glass-card bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-fuchsia-50 border-purple-200">
                <CardHeader>
                  <CardTitle className="text-lg text-purple-900">Strategic Implications for Clairvoyance-CX</CardTitle>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <div className="space-y-3">
                    <div className="flex items-start gap-3">
                      <AlertCircle className="h-5 w-5 text-rose-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0" />
                      <div>
                        <h4 className="font-semibold text-rose-900 text-sm">Digital Friction Points</h4>
                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-700">Technical issues with apps (Sahatna) and HIE (Malaffi) are primary drivers of negative sentiment and high-volume troubleshooting searches.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div className="flex items-start gap-3">
                      <Sparkles className="h-5 w-5 text-fuchsia-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0" />
                      <div>
                        <h4 className="font-semibold text-fuchsia-900 text-sm">Wellness/Aesthetic Convergence</h4>
                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-700">Significant market for content and services bridging &quot;beauty&quot; and &quot;clinical health,&quot; particularly in K-beauty and supplements.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div className="flex items-start gap-3">
                      <Shield className="h-5 w-5 text-orange-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0" />
                      <div>
                        <h4 className="font-semibold text-orange-900 text-sm">Regulatory Compliance Hurdles</h4>
                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-700">Insurance fine appeals and licensing exam preparation drive consistent search traffic among residents and professional expatriates.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div className="flex items-start gap-3">
                      <Target className="h-5 w-5 text-emerald-600 mt-0.5 shrink-0" />
                      <div>
                        <h4 className="font-semibold text-emerald-900 text-sm">Clinical Specialization Demand</h4>
                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-700">Oncology, Cardiology, and Obesity Management are the &quot;Big Three&quot; clinical drivers in both policy and consumer search intent.</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>

              {/* Future Outlook */}
              <Card className="glass-card">
                <CardHeader>
                  <CardTitle className="text-lg text-cyan-900 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <TrendingUp className="h-5 w-5" />
                    Future Outlook: Path Toward 2030
                  </CardTitle>
                </CardHeader>
                <CardContent>
                  <div className="space-y-3">
                    <p className="text-sm text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
                      As Abu Dhabi moves toward its 2030 vision, the healthcare sector will be defined by the <strong>&quot;Bioconvergence&quot;</strong> of technology and biology. The integration of the Emirati Reference Genome into daily clinical practice will make personalized medicine a reality for the majority.
                    </p>

                    <div className="grid gap-2 md:grid-cols-3">
                      <div className="p-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-denim-50 rounded-lg border border-cyan-200">
                        <h4 className="font-semibold text-cyan-900 text-sm mb-1">AI-Clinician Support</h4>
                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-700">PHI platform evolves to help doctors anticipate risks before acute symptoms manifest</p>
                      </div>

                      <div className="p-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-fuchsia-50 rounded-lg border border-purple-200">
                        <h4 className="font-semibold text-purple-900 text-sm mb-1">Digitally Fluent Workforce</h4>
                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-700">Training on health media systems and mandatory Malaffi use for homecare patients</p>
                      </div>

                      <div className="p-3 bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 rounded-lg border border-emerald-200">
                        <h4 className="font-semibold text-emerald-900 text-sm mb-1">Silent Guardian</h4>
                        <p className="text-xs text-slate-700">Background layer of intelligent technology ensuring longer, healthier, more productive lives</p>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>
            </div>
          </GlassPanel>
        </TabsContent>

        {/* File 23: Strategic Analysis - Narrative, Human, and Operational Assets */}
        <TabsContent value="strategic" className="space-y-6">
          <GlassPanel title="Strategic Analysis" description="Structural re-engineering of Abu Dhabi healthcare ecosystem (2024-2026)">
            <div className="space-y-6">
